This paper deals with machine learning techniques for imitation learning and goal-conditioned reinforcement learning, which are subfields of artificial intelligence and robotics. The paper also discusses the use of density estimation, which is a common technique in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
